el resto de las poblaciones del ambiente chaque\u00f1o. 4.9. Estudiar la situaci\u00f3n de la especie en Bolivia. Acci\u00f3n 4.1. Implementar estudios enfocados en conocer la distribuci\u00f3n de la especie a diferentes escalas espaciales, incluyendo escalas peque\u00f1as. Responsable: Jeffrey Thompson. Plazo: 5 a\u00f1os. Colaboradores: Micaela Camino, Anthony Giordano, Rosa L. Cuellar. 72 Acci\u00f3n 4.2. Identificar las variables de importancia que se asocian con la presencia del Tagu\u00e1.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e53a4b29-7640-4f76-9e6d-f695d7fb1f6f": {"__data__": {"id_": "e53a4b29-7640-4f76-9e6d-f695d7fb1f6f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/pecari-del-chaco-o-tagua-catagonus-wagneri", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Pecar\u00ed del Chaco o Tagu\u00e1 Catagonus wagneri", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/pecari-del-chaco-o-tagua-catagonus-wagneri", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "76913e5e533d9f46be8fe497f58c6a4bb0d0f3cd0bebcdd9411fe53eb8af5f64"}, "2": {"node_id": "f596e46f-22aa-4722-b855-0bff20e7e1f0", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/pecari-del-chaco-o-tagua-catagonus-wagneri", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "ecb871bba1e93809e9e674b8acd5855e981f21374bccb7fc9372d7e233311b1